{"tid":1978392,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"一人一個曼德拉效應的例子：隊長小翼","createTime":"2020-04-18T16:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T07:27:27.000Z","uid":81028,"like":3,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"26619da0a5e2ffe3abf960947be6d48929c07116","tid":1978392,"uid":81028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:16:12.000Z","msg":"剛剛viuTV 播放《隊長小翼》，全部人物的人名都唔同曬，我明明記得主角叫&ldquo;戴志偉&rdquo;。宜家連維基百科都改左叫：<strong>大空翼</strong>（日語：大空 翼，平假名：おおぞら つばさ），日本漫畫《足球小將翼》的主角。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOCSNeG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOCSNeG.png&h=0208bb81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人有其他類似的曼德拉效應經歷分享？"},{"pid":"fc7b0be90430be8cf887c10a09c604d8a9bc6938","tid":1978392,"uid":40397,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:18:50.000Z","msg":"以前d 漫畫譯名想用番一d 比較近香港會用既人名，所以先改到咁，而家直接用番日本原名啫，都唔算好特別啦"},{"pid":"4acba66685f1b7c60c28804aa859ddfcafb7eb24","tid":1978392,"uid":26038,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:20:17.000Z","msg":"我記得叫太空翼<br />\n而家大空翼？！"},{"pid":"e370de27c04f3dffb90204cda922a356b8ebcb80","tid":1978392,"uid":28547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"小學時叫戴志偉，張衛健唱主題曲<br />\n大學果時叫戴翅偉，送禮勤唱主題曲"},{"pid":"820c1af10a0df044f0dca47689ad0bbd25a2590e","tid":1978392,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T21:36:37.000Z","msg":"我成日認住葵新伍好撚勁<br />\n（其實只係跑狗）"},{"pid":"0ef343586466aac00a90665fb2358829422b58b1","tid":1978392,"uid":50366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:53:30.000Z","msg":"我淨係記得大空翼出到倒掛金勾<br />\n點知三杉淳，岬太郎，連果個日向小次郎都出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e15b83a9db23d9bc51ab4f0e2ac8c915575f604","tid":1978392,"uid":81028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"我記得有&rdquo;衝力射球&rdquo;, 你地有無印象?"},{"pid":"8f2